- **Sequential mode**: At each Phase 2 task boundary (after a task completes, before the next one starts), check `Tasks` for new non-NeedsReview tasks not yet seen. Merge them into the execution queue ordered by their position in the controller's `Tasks` ObservableCollection — so a user reorder (MoveUp/MoveDown) is naturally honoured.

